<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";background: #EEDD82;">1961–1970</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><strong class="selflink">A Canticle for Leibowitz</strong></i> by <a href="/wiki/Walter_M._Miller,_Jr." title="Walter M. Miller, Jr.">Walter M. Miller, Jr.</a> (1961)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Stranger_in_a_Strange_Land" title="Stranger in a Strange Land">Stranger in a Strange Land</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a> (1962)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Man_in_the_High_Castle" title="The Man in the High Castle">The Man in the High Castle</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Philip_K._Dick" title="Philip K. Dick">Philip K. Dick</a> (1963)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Way_Station_(novel)" title="Way Station (novel)">Here Gather the Stars</a></i> (aka: <i>Way Station</i>) by <a href="/wiki/Clifford_D._Simak" title="Clifford D. Simak">Clifford D. Simak</a> (1964)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Wanderer_(Fritz_Leiber_novel)" title="The Wanderer (Fritz Leiber novel)">The Wanderer</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Fritz_Leiber" title="Fritz Leiber">Fritz Leiber</a> (1965)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Dune_(novel)" title="Dune (novel)">Dune</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Frank_Herbert" title="Frank Herbert">Frank Herbert</a> and <i><a href="/wiki/...And_Call_Me_Conrad" title="...And Call Me Conrad" class="mw-redirect">...And Call Me Conrad</a></i> (aka: <i>This Immortal</i>) by <a href="/wiki/Roger_Zelazny" title="Roger Zelazny">Roger Zelazny</a> (1966)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Moon_Is_a_Harsh_Mistress" title="The Moon Is a Harsh Mistress">The Moon Is a Harsh Mistress</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a> (1967)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Lord_of_Light" title="Lord of Light">Lord of Light</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Roger_Zelazny" title="Roger Zelazny">Roger Zelazny</a> (1968)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Stand_on_Zanzibar" title="Stand on Zanzibar">Stand on Zanzibar</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/John_Brunner_(novelist)" title="John Brunner (novelist)">John Brunner</a> (1969)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Left_Hand_of_Darkness" title="The Left Hand of Darkness">The Left Hand of Darkness</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Ursula_K._Le_Guin" title="Ursula K. Le Guin">Ursula K. Le Guin</a> (1970)</span></p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
